Hardware Requirements
Component	Description
Computers (Min. 2‚Äì4)	LAN-enabled PCs or laptops
Layer 2 Switch	Device for connecting PCs within the LAN
LAN Cards	Installed in each computer
RJ-45 Connectors	8-pin connectors for UTP cables
